OL,5,G1010 Marcus Wareing: Tales from a..
OL,6,     FThis series follows Marcus - chef
OL,7,     Fextraordinaire and successful
OL,8,     Frestaurateur - as he follows his
OL,9,     Fdream of living, and cooking, in
OL,10,     Fthe English countryside.
OL,11,G1050 John & Lisa's Weekend Kitchen
OL,12,     FJohn Torode and Lisa Faulkner
OL,13,     Fprepare Glamorgan sausages with
OL,14,     Fchilli jam, indulgent roast
OL,15,     Fchicken with cranberry stuffing
OL,16,     Fand 'naughty' mash, and the
OL,17,     F'ultimate' nut roast.
